                    "text": "Unlike some fey, redcaps don\u2019t\nembody a particular natural\nfeature or environment, so they\ncan be found almost anywhere.\nThey tend to prefer areas that\nallow them to hide or at least\nget behind cover with their\nquick movement, such as\nforests, mountains,\nand underground\ntunnels and\ncaverns.",
